main event: Officials at Biggs Air Force Base in Texas reported sightings of 2 to 11 unidentified flying objects on radar, which disappeared in close proximity to each other.
interesting points: The objects were sighted on radar but visual sightings were unsuccessful,The report noted that this type of disappearance is unusual as objects typically vanish one at a time,There was a possibility that the radar returns could have been caused by a flight of helicopters or ducks,The sighting lasted approximately 5 minutes,Final conclusions remained inconclusive with no satisfactory explanation provided.
witness description: military personnel at Biggs Air Force Base
